GoldenEye::
She looked up at Terrorsaur. She saw two of them standing before her. 
She tried to stand up, but fell down. "I, I'll be ok. I think. Ohh, 
my aching head." She tried to stand up again, and grabbed one of the 
Terrorsaur's shoulder. She steadied herself and stood there a moment. 
Her vision was still burred and her head pounded.

> Terrorsaur:
